---
---
<section class="pain-points">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>If any of this sounds familiar...</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Data Safety form keeps rejecting your app</h3>
        <p>Google's Data Safety questionnaire is where 60% of submissions die. Wrong answers trigger automatic rejection with vague feedback.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Stuck in closed testing for weeks</h3>
        <p>The 14-day, 20-tester requirement kills momentum. Most indie devs never make it to production rollout.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Suspended without a clear reason</h3>
        <p>Google's enforcement notices are cryptic. Without policy expertise, your appeal almost always fails.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pain-points {
    background: var(--bg);
    padding-block: 100px;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding-inline: 24px;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    text-align: left;
    margin: 0 0 48px 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--soft);
    border: 0.5px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 24px;
    transition: border-color 150ms ease, color 150ms ease;
  }

  .card:hover {
    border-color: var(--line-strong);
  }

  .card h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 12px 0 0 0;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .pain-points {
      padding-block: 60px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
    }
  }
</style>
